<p rend="nobreak">

<milestone unit="sentence" n="638" /> --Absconded from the farm of <persName n="Powell,Mister,Joseph,F.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00471" reg="default:Powell,Joseph,F.,," authname="powell,joseph,f."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Joseph</foreName> <foreName full="yes">F.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Powell</surname></persName>, <num value="1">one</num> or <measure n="2miles" type="distance">two miles</measure> west of this city, about the last of <dateStruct value="-06-" full="yes" authname="--06"><month reg="06" full="yes">June</month></dateStruct>, without any cause whatever, a likely negro man, named <persName><foreName full="yes">Edmund</foreName></persName>, about <unclear><num value="1">1</num></unclear> years of age, supposed to be <measure n="5feet" type="distance">five feet</measure> high, genteel, figure, quite intelligent, has a full suit of hair, large, full eyes, big mouth, thick lips, good looking teeth, speaks quick but sometimes affects an impediment is speaking; no particular mark remembered.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="639" />He is supposed to have hired himself to some of the companies near <placeName key="tgn,7013964" n="1.000 5" reg="richmond, richmond, virginia" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName> as a free boy, or may have left with some that have been sept away — I will pay the above reward of <measure n="25dollars" type="currency">$25</measure>, if taken <measure n="50miles" type="distance">fifty miles</measure>, <measure n="100dollars" type="currency">$100</measure> if taken out of the <rs>State</rs>, and <measure n="10dollars" type="currency">$10</measure> if found in or near this city, and delivered to said <persName n="Powell,Mister,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00472" reg="nearbymention:Powell,Joseph,F.,," authname="powell,joseph,f."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Powell</surname></persName>, or put in jail so that I can get him again [an <num value="5">5</num>--3t*] E. N Drewey. </p> </div3> </div2> 
