<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1087" /> in accordance with the act of <date value="1861-08-26" authname="1861-08-26">August 26th, 1861,</date> Sealed Proposals for furnishing this Department with Stationery will be received until the <date value="07-22" authname="--07-22">22d day of July</date> Proximo.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="1088" />Stationers are requested to name the terms upon which they will deliver the following articles, and are required to accompany their proposals with specimen samples of the same: </p> 
